            <div class="content">
                <p>
                    Mental health, even after being well known, is something that still gets treated as a taboo. Sometimes, it is even hard for people to accept that them or their loved ones are going through a mental health problem.<br><br>
                    <b>'Dear Zindagi'</b> is an attempt to address our own lives in optimistic ways, to develop a sensitive observation towards our surroundings and keep a check on our closed ones. So that, we are ready when they need our help the most!
                </p>
