        <div id="importance" class="block">

            <div class="extra">
            <div class="heading">
                <div>Importance of Mental Health</div>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <p>
                    It is simple! Mental & physical health are closely related. Prolonged battle with mental issues can show their effect on physical. And thus, they combinedly might affect our productivity, work life, personal relations, and overall, our happiness!<br><br>
                    To be happy and healthy should be our priority. As we are caretakers of our own selves. We should be the first person to love ourselves.<br><br>
                    And that is why, keeping a check on our mental health is very important!
                </p>
